Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.42,0:00:06.69,Default,GENSEI,0,0,0,,I hear a student congress was held the other day,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.45,0:00:13.01,Default,GENSEI,0,0,0,,with Masachika and the heiress of \NTaniyama Industries participating.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.01,0:00:13.71,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.14,0:00:18.16,Default,GENSEI,0,0,0,,She took you to the wire in your \Nmiddle school presidential election,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.16,0:00:20.19,Default,GENSEI,0,0,0,,so I expected good things from her.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.98,0:00:24.65,Default,GENSEI,0,0,0,,But it seems she left \Nin the middle of the debate?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.65,0:00:26.83,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,She must have had her reasons.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.24,0:00:34.84,Default,GENSEI,0,0,0,,Whatever her reasons, it has resulted\Nin Masachika's campaign gaining legitimacy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.20,0:00:39.90,Default,GENSEI,0,0,0,,Listen, no matter who you are up against, \Nyou aren't allowed to lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.90,0:00:42.66,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,I realize that, Grandfather.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.50,0:00:46.92,Default,GENSEI,0,0,0,,You may not be as gifted as Masachika,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.35,0:00:51.66,Default,GENSEI,0,0,0,,but you know that with great gifts \Ncome great responsibilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.07,0:00:54.36,Default,GENSEI,0,0,0,,Responsibilities he ran away from.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.87,0:00:59.47,Default,GENSEI,0,0,0,,He was born with unrivaled talents \Nand into unmatched privilege,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.47,0:01:01.10,Default,GENSEI,0,0,0,,but he threw it all away.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.18,0:01:07.12,Default,GENSEI,0,0,0,,Losing to him, of all people, \Nis absolutely not an option.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.58,0:01:09.75,Default,GENSEI,0,0,0,,Are we clear, Yuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.75,0:01:11.71,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,Of course, Grandfather.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.91,0:01:15.94,Default,YUMI,0,0,0,,Yuki-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.88,0:01:19.76,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,Is something the matter, Mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.44,0:01:24.34,Default,YUMI,0,0,0,,Are you and Masachika-san still as close as ever?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.34,0:01:26.02,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,Yes, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.08,0:01:28.36,Default,YUMI,0,0,0,,Good to hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.36,0:01:31.96,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,Uh, what about him?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.96,0:01:33.38,Default,YUMI,0,0,0,,Nothing. Never mind me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.11,0:01:37.02,Default,YUMI,0,0,0,,You have Chinese class now, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.02,0:01:39.03,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,Yes, online.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.59,0:01:43.04,Default,YUMI,0,0,0,,Good luck with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.54,0:01:44.42,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.82,0:01:49.68,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,Ayano.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.68,0:01:51.17,Default,AYANO,0,0,0,,Yes, Yuki-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.17,0:01:52.67,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,Let me hug you for a sec!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.67,0:01:54.68,Default,AYANO,0,0,0,,As you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.53,0:02:05.93,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,Okay, I'm all better now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.93,0:02:07.63,Default,AYANO,0,0,0,,Are you done?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.63,0:02:09.56,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,Yeah, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.56,0:02:10.65,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,Man...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.65,0:02:13.20,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,Tiddies truly are great.
