Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.04,0:03:46.99,top,BOY 1,0,0,0,,Heya, Kuze.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.38,0:03:49.50,top,BOY 1,0,0,0,,You did amazing in student congress last week.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.86,0:03:54.92,Default,BOY A,0,0,0,,I thought Taniyama-san had it in the bag \Nafter hearing her argument, but whew.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.92,0:03:57.38,Default,BOY B,0,0,0,,How much of that did you have planned out?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.68,0:04:01.02,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Hey, at least let me put my bag down.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.01,0:04:04.84,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Morning, Alya.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.84,0:04:06.39,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Yes, good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.72,0:04:09.83,italics,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Wow, business as usual, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.31,0:04:15.62,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Alya, these guys wanna hear more \Nabout your exploits last week.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.62,0:04:16.36,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.36,0:04:19.29,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Go ahead and get the deets from her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.29,0:04:21.83,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,I must go. My gacha needs me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.71,0:04:33.36,Default,HIKARU,0,0,0,,Kujo-san, did you write your own speech?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.36,0:04:37.94,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Huh? Oh, yes, that was me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.94,0:04:40.00,Default,HIKARU,0,0,0,,Wow, I'm impressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.00,0:04:42.69,Default,HIKARU,0,0,0,,You're a great orator too, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.69,0:04:45.13,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Th-Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.14,0:04:49.28,Default,BOY A,0,0,0,,Was not asking questions part of your strategy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.28,0:04:53.36,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Right. We'd decided not to.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.36,0:04:56.04,Default,BOY B,0,0,0,,What about Kuze taking over partway, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.04,0:04:59.11,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,I wasn't expecting that, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.11,0:05:03.01,Default,BOY G,0,0,0,,I can't believe Taniyama \Nstraight up ran away, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.01,0:05:05.24,Default,BOY D,0,0,0,,She was the one who started it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.55,0:05:07.08,Default,BOY D,0,0,0,,Talk about pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.17,0:05:10.07,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Kuze-kun, a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.07,0:05:10.74,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.52,0:05:13.11,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.11,0:05:16.87,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Oh, right. We had student council \Nbusiness to take care of.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.87,0:05:19.16,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Sorry, we'll pick this back up later.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.87,0:05:19.63,sign_generic,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\bordo\b1\c&H3F4645&\frx14\fry54\frz337.1\pos(343,145)}Student Council Office
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.79,0:05:21.38,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.38,0:05:22.58,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.86,0:05:27.42,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Did Taniyama getting ridiculed \Nbother you so much?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.42,0:05:29.14,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,I mean, she was just...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.53,0:05:32.72,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Yeah, you and I know why she did what she did.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.17,0:05:39.49,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,But remember, we did nothing wrong. \NWe simply fought fair and square.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.49,0:05:44.17,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,There's no need to let what people say \Nabout her bother us, is there?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.17,0:05:45.24,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,I get that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.86,0:05:48.99,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,But we didn't actually beat them.\NThey simply forfeited.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.77,0:05:54.93,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,What's your plan, then? \NLet's assume we help her save face.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.93,0:05:58.42,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,That'll mean our student congress \Nvictory goes to waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.85,0:06:01.52,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,I know...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.27,0:06:05.87,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,That's what I would say if I were \Nputting our interests first.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.43,0:06:08.11,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,But who cares about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.11,0:06:08.88,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.88,0:06:11.98,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,What matters is what you want to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.67,0:06:16.27,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Well, I want to help Taniyama-san, obviously.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.27,0:06:18.16,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,But that'd be...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.16,0:06:21.23,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Okay, gotcha. Then that's what we'll do.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.23,0:06:21.90,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.90,0:06:22.89,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.89,0:06:25.62,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Of course. No point letting this drag out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.62,0:06:29.66,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,We'll sort this mess out and head into \Nthe closing ceremony with a clear conscience.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.78,0:06:33.71,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. I know this will \Ncreate more work for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.71,0:06:35.22,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.22,0:06:37.25,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Like I said, I'm here for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.21,0:06:40.16,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Kuze-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.30,0:06:46.88,italics,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,I sense a disturbance in the air.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.15,0:06:48.52,Default,CHISATO,0,0,0,,Scoot in!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.52,0:06:50.26,Default,TOYA,0,0,0,,E-Easy for you to say!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.26,0:06:52.98,italics,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Wow, a situation straight out of a rom-com.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.27,0:06:58.14,italics,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,As their junior, the right thing to do here \Nis to pretend I saw nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.98,0:07:05.52,italics,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Whoa, wait a second.\NIs a rom-com scene starting over here too?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.28,0:07:08.58,italics,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Welp, we got a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.58,0:07:10.66,italics,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,In many different ways all at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.66,0:07:17.21,italics,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,All I can do now is divert \Nher attention elsewhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.41,0:07:18.79,sign_generic,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,1)\fnComic Sans MS\b1\an7\fs28\3c&H440B02&}ELSEWHERE
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.58,0:07:24.50,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,How long are you gonna keep hiding, \NPrez, Sarashina-senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.63,0:07:26.51,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.40,0:07:32.47,Default,TOYA,0,0,0,,Sorry about that. We missed \Nour chance to announce our presence.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.08,0:07:37.22,Default,CHISATO,0,0,0,,Yeah. We were just looking \Nfor something we dropped on the floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.01,0:07:43.60,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Well, how about we pretend none of us \Nsaw or heard anything here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.60,0:07:46.67,Default,TOYA,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah, good idea. Let's go with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.60,0:07:49.74,sign_generic,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\b1\bord0\c&H7E7177&\frx4\fry2\frz358.2\move(384,259,384,268)}Word of the Week\N"Thoughtfulness"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.67,0:07:48.41,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Glad we have an agreement.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.41,0:07:49.74,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Let's go, Alya.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.56,0:07:55.54,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Er, um... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.54,0:07:58.12,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,I just remembered something I need to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.12,0:08:01.33,sign_generic,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\fs8\b1\pos(108,36)\3c&HCCD3D5&\c&H5D6468&}Student Council Office
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.31,0:08:06.54,Default,GIRL 3,0,0,0,,Say, Nonoa.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.99,0:08:09.69,Default,GIRL 3,0,0,0,,Did you see Phamel's newest collection? \NPretty cool, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.73,0:08:13.52,Default,NONOA,0,0,0,,I dunno... Nothing really grabbed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.52,0:08:17.70,Default,GIRL 3,0,0,0,,Oh... Guess I'll pass too, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.70,0:08:21.89,italics,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Ugh, normies! Not going \Nanywhere near them!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.34,0:08:24.30,Default,GIRL 2,0,0,0,,That aside, Nonoa.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.30,0:08:27.90,Default,GIRL 2,0,0,0,,Wanna come to my house party on Sunday?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.90,0:08:29.85,Default,NONOA,0,0,0,,But we have exams coming up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.85,0:08:32.03,Default,GIRL 2,0,0,0,,We could also have a study sesh.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.03,0:08:33.22,Default,NONOA,0,0,0,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.22,0:08:36.15,Default,GIRL 2,0,0,0,,Y'know, aren't you being kinda distant lately?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.72,0:08:39.44,Default,NONOA,0,0,0,,I'm just kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.44,0:08:42.04,Default,NONOA,0,0,0,,Count me in for the party.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.04,0:08:43.37,Default,GIRL 2,0,0,0,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.37,0:08:46.04,Default,BOY X,0,0,0,,What? I'll go if Nonoa's going.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.44,0:08:48.15,Default,NONOA,0,0,0,,D'you need something, Kuzecchi?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.15,0:08:51.17,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Uh, y-yeah, kinda.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.17,0:08:54.24,Default,NONOA,0,0,0,,Oh, can't talk about it here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.24,0:08:56.55,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,I'd prefer not to, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.89,0:08:58.17,Default,NONOA,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.89,0:09:01.05,Default,NONOA,0,0,0,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.05,0:09:04.68,Default,NONOA,0,0,0,,I'm all ears if you wanna ask me out, \Nbut that's not what you're here for, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.68,0:09:05.60,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.60,0:09:07.44,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Wait, you're all ears?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.44,0:09:12.57,Default,NONOA,0,0,0,,I mean, I'm single right now, \Nand I don't really mind you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.57,0:09:17.65,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Uh, maybe go out \Nwith someone you actually like.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.65,0:09:21.46,Default,NONOA,0,0,0,,I've never dated anyone I really liked.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.46,0:09:23.70,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Talk about a problematic statement.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.05,0:09:28.46,Default,NONOA,0,0,0,,Can you blame me? I don't get \Nall that love and romance stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.64,0:09:32.84,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Far be it from me to meddle in your affairs,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.17,0:09:37.06,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,but you should probably try \Nto avoid selling yourself short.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.48,0:09:41.57,Default,NONOA,0,0,0,,Sayacchi told me the exact same thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.57,0:09:43.71,Default,NONOA,0,0,0,,It came with a bonus slap, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.71,0:09:44.85,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.15,0:09:47.68,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Taniyama's the type to throw hands, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.68,0:09:50.12,Default,NONOA,0,0,0,,Oh, uh, that was probably a one-off.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.38,0:09:54.27,Default,NONOA,0,0,0,,Anyway, how can I help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.27,0:09:58.05,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Right. You know how people \Nare talking shit about Taniyama?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.05,0:10:00.87,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,I'm wondering if we can put a stop to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.17,0:10:04.75,Default,NONOA,0,0,0,,Oh? I didn't think it'd bother you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.75,0:10:07.40,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Well, it bothers my partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.40,0:10:09.12,Default,NONOA,0,0,0,,Ah, I get it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.83,0:10:12.82,Default,NONOA,0,0,0,,That's so sweet of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.90,0:10:17.95,Default,NONOA,0,0,0,,So? Why come to me about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.95,0:10:21.14,Default,NONOA,0,0,0,,You do realize I'm the enemy, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.14,0:10:22.91,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,"Enemy," huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.91,0:10:27.35,Default,NONOA,0,0,0,,I'm sure you noticed that \NI had plants in the audience.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.35,0:10:29.53,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Of course I noticed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.53,0:10:34.87,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,I can't believe you'd risk destroying \Nyour friendships like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.73,0:10:39.36,Default,NONOA,0,0,0,,Frankly, I'm not attached to \Nany of my friends other than Sayacchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.75,0:10:42.87,Default,NONOA,0,0,0,,I don't really care if I lose 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.86,0:10:45.74,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Can I ask you something?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.95,0:10:50.40,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,People like Taniyama, \Nwith a fire burning within,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.40,0:10:53.45,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,should be a total mystery to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.45,0:10:55.09,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Why're you so attached to her, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.09,0:10:57.81,Default,NONOA,0,0,0,,Oh, you've got it the wrong way around.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.81,0:11:02.22,Default,NONOA,0,0,0,,She intrigues me {\i1}because{\i0} she's such \Na mystery, and that's why I want her around.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.22,0:11:03.80,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Is that how it works?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.80,0:11:10.10,Default,NONOA,0,0,0,,Surely you get how it feels to be drawn \Nto someone with a fire you don't possess.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.05,0:11:16.41,Default,NONOA,0,0,0,,Now, we're both miserable cynics attached \Nto our shining-rays-of-positivity partners.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.41,0:11:18.53,Default,NONOA,0,0,0,,Why don't we get our \Nmiserable little scheme rolling?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.53,0:11:22.24,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,I don't know if I would go that far, but okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.94,0:11:24.52,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,My proposal is simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.52,0:11:30.44,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,We spread a rumor giving a plausible \Nexplanation to why Taniyama left that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.44,0:11:34.63,Default,NONOA,0,0,0,,To make it seem like she \Ndidn't run away from a fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.08,0:11:38.58,Default,NONOA,0,0,0,,Are you sure? \NIt'll bring your victory into question.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.58,0:11:40.24,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,That's fine by us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.24,0:11:41.51,Default,NONOA,0,0,0,,Huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.02,0:11:48.27,Default,NONOA,0,0,0,,Well, she's my partner. It's my job \Nto clean up after her to begin with.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.73,0:11:52.43,Default,NONOA,0,0,0,,So yeah, we have a deal. See ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.43,0:11:54.03,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.92,0:11:59.57,italics,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,You know what this reminds me of? That manga \Nscene where you summon your trusty spy
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.57,0:12:03.16,italics,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,and say, "Follow 'em. \NMake sure not to be spotted."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.19,0:12:05.18,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Ayano.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.18,0:12:06.37,Default,AYANO,0,0,0,,Yes, Masachika-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.37,0:12:08.39,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Whoa! Why are you here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.39,0:12:12.12,Default,AYANO,0,0,0,,Huh? Because you summoned me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.74,0:12:15.92,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,Don't go ignoring me now, Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.92,0:12:18.92,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Seriously, what are you two doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.59,0:12:25.18,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,Oh, we noticed you approaching \NLady Nonoa, an enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.47,0:12:28.84,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,So we hid behind the teacher's desk \Nto eavesdrop on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.84,0:12:30.43,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,The damn desk again?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.95,0:12:33.21,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,And? What's the real story?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.21,0:12:35.40,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,We were pretending to have a secret meeting,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.40,0:12:38.32,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,not knowing that an actual \Nsecret meeting would take place here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.32,0:12:40.64,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,What is {\i1}wrong{\i0} with you two?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.09,0:12:42.82,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Kuze-kun? Are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.30,0:12:48.83,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.12,0:12:53.16,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Alya-san? You're not jumping \Nto conclusions, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.16,0:12:58.84,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,What do you mean? There's nothing wrong \Nwith three childhood friends hanging out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.12,0:13:00.93,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Well, enjoy yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.93,0:13:02.09,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,A-Alya!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.59,0:13:06.59,sign_generic,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\pos(321,310.727)\bord1.4\3c&H202423&\c&HE5F0EB&}Bah! Leaving me out of the fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.79,0:13:09.09,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,Bro...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.09,0:13:10.96,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,You just {\i1}know{\i0} she went,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.96,0:13:16.29,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,"I made lunch for Kuze-kun to repay him \Nfor helping me in the debate. Where is he?"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.29,0:13:19.98,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,and looked for you all over school, \Nonly to be hit in the face with disappointment.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.98,0:13:23.30,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Quit fabricating the most cliched of setups!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.08,0:13:37.85,flashback,SAYAKA,0,0,0,,It was a different boy last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.85,0:13:39.49,flashback,NONOA,0,0,0,,Was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.49,0:13:43.09,flashback,NONOA,0,0,0,,Well, he's my boyfriend now, \Nso I figured why not.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.82,0:13:51.93,flashback,NONOA,0,0,0,,Quit selling yourself short!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.30,0:13:54.58,flashback,NONOA,0,0,0,,You need to value yourself more!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.46,0:13:59.94,Default,NONOA,0,0,0,,She didn't have to get that mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.86,0:14:02.94,Default,GIRL 3,0,0,0,,You're finally back, Nonoa.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.34,0:14:04.97,Default,GIRL 3,0,0,0,,What was that all about?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.97,0:14:07.95,Default,NONOA,0,0,0,,Oh, he was asking about Sayacchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.32,0:14:11.94,Default,NONOA,0,0,0,,He wanted to know why\Nshe skipped school today.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.94,0:14:13.71,Default,GIRL 3,0,0,0,,Taniyama's skipping today?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.71,0:14:15.87,Default,GIRL 2,0,0,0,,Feeling down over losing the debate?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.87,0:14:19.21,Default,NONOA,0,0,0,,Oh, nah. It's my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.21,0:14:23.95,Default,NONOA,0,0,0,,Besides, she only left the debate \Nbecause she was mad at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.95,0:14:25.05,Default,BOY X,0,0,0,,H-Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.05,0:14:26.09,Default,GIRL 2,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.09,0:14:33.57,Default,NONOA,0,0,0,,She found out halfway through student congress\N that I had plants in the audience.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.57,0:14:34.79,Default,NONOA,0,0,0,,Y'know how it goes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.05,0:14:40.31,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Again, I really just happened \Nto run into Yuki and Ayano there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.73,0:14:41.81,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.13,0:14:44.11,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Not buying it, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.11,0:14:47.23,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Please, you don't need to make excuses.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.23,0:14:50.07,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,I'm glad you three \Nchildhood friends are so close.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.87,0:14:53.86,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Oh, all that aside,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.86,0:14:56.90,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,will you study with me after school today?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.90,0:14:59.30,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,You? Study? What kind of sick joke is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.30,0:15:01.58,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Now that's just rude, plain and simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.59,0:15:09.89,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Um... Alya-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.89,0:15:10.84,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.20,0:15:13.63,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Aren't you sitting a little close?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.63,0:15:15.47,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Is that a problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.47,0:15:17.47,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Not really, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.85,0:15:21.35,italics,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,I guess it's fine as long as nobody s...ees?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.35,0:15:25.11,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,My, I apologize. I should have knocked.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.47,0:15:27.61,italics,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Sister of mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.12,0:15:30.60,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,Are you preparing for exams?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.60,0:15:34.12,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,If you don't mind, may we join you as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.87,0:15:35.49,sign_generic,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\pos(321,310.727)\bord1.4\3c&H202423&\c&HE5F0EB&}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.78,0:15:40.01,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Alya? You heard her. What do you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.01,0:15:43.24,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Sure. I don't see a reason to refuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.24,0:15:44.00,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.40,0:15:45.93,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,Thank you kindly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.50,0:15:48.25,sign_generic,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\pos(321,310.727)\bord1.4\3c&H202423&\c&HE5F0EB&}I'd prefer we were alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.50,0:15:51.38,italics,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,You cutie, you! Quit being so adorable!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.97,0:16:01.18,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,All you've been doing is reading the solutions.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.18,0:16:03.85,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Is that really going to help you prepare?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.85,0:16:07.78,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Tearing my hair out over problems \NI don't get is a waste of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.78,0:16:11.65,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Time better spent \Ngetting the solutions into my head.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.65,0:16:14.58,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,How will you learn to put theory \Ninto practice like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.38,0:16:16.94,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,Not to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.94,0:16:19.61,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,Masachika-kun's always been like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.61,0:16:21.02,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,Right, Ayano?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.02,0:16:25.17,Default,AYANO,0,0,0,,That's right. This is how Masachika-sama \Nhas always studied.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.69,0:16:31.57,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Ayano? Is there something you don't get?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.57,0:16:33.20,Default,AYANO,0,0,0,,Oh, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.77,0:16:36.18,Default,AYANO,0,0,0,,Actually, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.46,0:16:37.45,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.45,0:16:41.63,Default,AYANO,0,0,0,,No, I couldn't bother you with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.63,0:16:44.94,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Relax. I'm not gonna \Nmock you over it or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.94,0:16:50.41,Default,AYANO,0,0,0,,Actually, I would prefer it if you berated me \Nand called me a useless waste of space.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.41,0:16:51.94,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Not happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.30,0:16:54.37,Default,AYANO,0,0,0,,Is that so...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.37,0:16:56.50,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Wait, why do you sound disappointed?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.50,0:17:00.33,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Are you three really just childhood friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.64,0:17:03.13,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Huh? Yeah, why?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.13,0:17:09.10,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,I mean, you seem awfully close, \Neven for childhood friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.82,0:17:13.34,Default,MASHA,0,0,0,,Hi there, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.59,0:17:21.07,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Mm! Masha-senpai's tea is simply divine!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.07,0:17:22.68,Default,MASHA,0,0,0,,My, what is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.01,0:17:27.06,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Oh, Sarashina-senpai apparently \Nconfiscated that book from someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.06,0:17:29.06,sign_generic,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\b1\3c&HF7FAF8&\c&H902D82&\fs15\frx4\fry350\frz349.6\pos(339,153)}Hypnosis for Dummies\N{\b0\fs13}Become a hypnotist today!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.06,0:17:29.06,sign_generic,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\fs10\3c&H9F5950&\c&HF7FAF8&\frz346.7\pos(305,345)}Kyoto Publishing
Dialogue: 1,0:17:27.67,0:17:29.06,Default,MASHA,0,0,0,,Huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.58,0:17:31.73,Default,MASHA,0,0,0,,Alya-chan, try it on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.73,0:17:32.57,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.57,0:17:34.84,Default,MASHA,0,0,0,,What? Why not?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.84,0:17:37.55,Default,MASHA,0,0,0,,I wanna try getting hypnotized!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.55,0:17:39.76,Default,MASHA,0,0,0,,I wanna, I wanna!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.76,0:17:41.77,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Again, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.77,0:17:44.45,Default,MASHA,0,0,0,,Then you do it, Kuze-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.45,0:17:45.88,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Huh? Why me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.88,0:17:48.96,Default,MASHA,0,0,0,,I mean, Alya-chan's being a big old meanie.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.38,0:17:51.54,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Well, if you insist.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.46,0:17:54.96,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,We start off with... hypnotic induction?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.46,0:17:54.96,sign_generic,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\b1\3c&HF7FAF8&\c&H902D82&\fs15\fry350\frz356.1\pos(207,223)}Hypnosis for Dummies\N{\b0\fs13}Become a hypnotist today!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.96,0:17:56.21,Default,MASHA,0,0,0,,Hype!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.21,0:18:00.45,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Uh... Okay, focus your eyes on my finger.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.45,0:18:01.42,Default,MASHA,0,0,0,,Your finger?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.42,0:18:02.53,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,That's what it says.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.53,0:18:03.72,Default,MASHA,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.69,0:18:11.48,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,"You feel your mind slowly go into a trance.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.48,0:18:14.22,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Keep your eyes right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.62,0:18:19.00,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,You're getting very, very sleepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.68,0:18:24.76,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,When I clap my hands, \Nyou will fall into a deep slumber."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.17,0:18:28.03,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Three, two, one... There.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.38,0:18:31.00,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Huh? Masha-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.00,0:18:35.51,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,Masha-senpai? Did you really get hypnotized?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.51,0:18:38.40,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah, very funny. Knock it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.32,0:18:40.64,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Masha?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.64,0:18:44.70,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,U-Uh, let me undo the hypnosis.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.70,0:18:45.77,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.04,0:18:50.20,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,"When I touch your shoulder, \Nyou will snap out of it."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.20,0:18:50.77,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,One...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.77,0:18:52.52,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Two, and there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.65,0:18:59.37,Default,MASHA,0,0,0,,Um... Why did you stop, Kuze-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.77,0:19:00.61,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.61,0:19:04.50,Default,MASHA,0,0,0,,Come on! You said you would clap your hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.50,0:19:07.41,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Wait, what? Do you not remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.41,0:19:09.20,Default,MASHA,0,0,0,,Remember what?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.20,0:19:12.29,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Seriously, Masha, that's not funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.29,0:19:17.05,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,Alya-san, why don't you have \NMasachika-kun hypnotize you too, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.74,0:19:18.81,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.74,0:19:18.81,top,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Wha?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.81,0:19:22.17,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,You'll know whether she's telling \Nthe truth or not one way or another.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.38,0:19:26.18,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,I'm ready. Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.18,0:19:27.60,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Are we seriously doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.60,0:19:31.40,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Get on with it. \NWe're putting an end to this farce.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.40,0:19:34.68,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Fine. Focus your eyes on my finger.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.97,0:19:37.57,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Way too easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.63,0:19:43.45,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,And why the heck did Masha-senpai \Nget hypnotized again?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.45,0:19:44.42,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Don't ask me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.42,0:19:47.01,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,For real? It's a booby-booty\Ngrabby-grabby free-for-all!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.01,0:19:48.33,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Don't say the quiet part out loud!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.37,0:19:51.96,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,Ready or not, it's time for otaku improv!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.91,0:20:01.47,sign_generic,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\an8\fnGeorgia\b1\3c&HD3DCDB&\c&H5A59BC&}Improv
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.96,0:19:54.75,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,The topic: You just hypnotized two hotties!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.75,0:19:57.31,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,What is the first suggestion you try?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.92,0:20:01.47,sign_generic,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\fnGeorgia\b1\fs15\3c&H4C3EB6&\c&HDDF6F7&\an7\pos(-11,49)\fade(300,1)}Otaku\h\h\h\h\h\h\hOtaku\h\h\h\h\hOtaku\h\h\h\h\h\hOtaku\h\h\h\h\h\hOtaku\h\h\h\h\h\h\hOtaku\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\hOtaku\h\h\h\h\h\hOtaku\h\h\h\h\hOtaku\h\h\h\h\h\h\hOtaku\h\h\h\h\h\hOtaku
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.31,0:19:58.83,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Mental age regression!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.83,0:20:01.47,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,Make them totally unrestrained \Nand have them strip!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.47,0:20:07.60,Default,AYANO,0,0,0,,U-Uh... Make them reveal their deepest, \Ndarkest secrets, maybe?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.00,0:20:10.94,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,"Make them unrestrained"? \NCouldn't you have been more specific?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.94,0:20:13.45,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,Yeah, well, your answer was just depraved.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.39,0:20:18.82,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,As for Ayano, not a bad answer, \Nbut it's a bit lacking in impact.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.82,0:20:23.73,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,Making them totally unrestrained \Nis the only right choice here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.73,0:20:26.69,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,They might even reveal their most \Nembarrassing secrets in that state.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.69,0:20:30.70,Default,AYANO,0,0,0,,Your answer even covered my suggestion? \NYou never cease to amaze.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.70,0:20:33.12,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,There. I win by majority vote.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.94,0:20:41.45,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,Alya-san, Masha-senpai, you two \Nwill become more and more unrestrained.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.45,0:20:46.14,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,Freed from the shackles of your inhibitions, \Nyou will lay your minds and bodies bare.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.14,0:20:53.14,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,Wait, what? For real?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.58,0:20:54.30,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Mm?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.75,0:20:56.65,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.18,0:21:05.51,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Tell me, Yuki. Why am I getting \Ninfinite head pats right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.62,0:21:08.66,Default,MASHA,0,0,0,,Good boy! Good girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.99,0:21:11.84,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,G-Gee, I wonder why.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.84,0:21:13.41,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Look me in the eye, culprit.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.71,0:21:18.38,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,I didn't expect Masha-senpai's \Nharem time to begin, not Masachika-kun's.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.38,0:21:20.51,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's{\i0} your problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.92,0:21:23.07,Default,MASHA,0,0,0,,Good boy, good girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.07,0:21:24.82,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Uh, Masha-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.82,0:21:26.97,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Could you let me go now?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.97,0:21:29.18,Default,MASHA,0,0,0,,What? Not happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.18,0:21:30.43,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Not happening, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.41,0:21:32.93,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,...oying.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.83,0:21:36.16,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Off with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.16,0:21:38.60,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,A-Alya? What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.20,0:21:50.69,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,Office worker who's a superstar at work \Nbut a slob at home, pictured in the morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.69,0:21:51.41,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.25,0:21:58.92,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Whoa, what? Why'd they both \Nstart taking off their clothes?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.92,0:22:04.92,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,Right, I did say they'd get more unrestrained \Nand lay their minds and bodies bare.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.25,0:22:11.54,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Er... When I touch your shoulder, \Nyou will snap out of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.54,0:22:13.43,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,One, two, and there!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.20,0:22:15.90,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Hey! That didn't work!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.31,0:22:21.47,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,Uh... When I touch your shoulder, \Nyou will snap out of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.47,0:22:23.78,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,One, two, and there.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.07,0:22:27.17,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,Yikes. This ain't working.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.17,0:22:28.94,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Are you serious?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.94,0:22:31.04,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,What are we gonna do about this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.04,0:22:35.08,Default,CHISATO,0,0,0,,Masha? I got done a while a... go...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.74,0:22:38.18,Default,CHISATO,0,0,0,,Uh, what's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.18,0:22:40.09,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,S-Sarashina-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.09,0:22:41.95,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,Well, you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.95,0:22:45.30,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,I tried out what was written \Nin the hypnosis book,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.59,0:22:48.09,sign_generic,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\b1\3c&HF7FAF8&\c&H7A3176&\fs10\frz354.5\frx32\fry354\pos(254,134)}Hypnosis for Dummies\N{\b0\fs8}Become a hypnotist today!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.59,0:22:48.09,sign_generic,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\fs8\3c&HA76755&\frz355.4\pos(228,217)\frx46\fry352}Kyoto Publishing
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.30,0:22:47.69,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,but now we can't snap them out of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.41,0:22:49.62,Default,CHISATO,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.62,0:22:51.59,Default,CHISATO,0,0,0,,Hup. Excuse me one moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.69,0:22:58.37,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Whoa, whoa, whoa! What?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.37,0:22:59.82,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,What the hell was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.29,0:23:01.38,Default,CHISATO,0,0,0,,A reset.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.38,0:23:02.17,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,What...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.53,0:23:09.92,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Huh? Why am I on the couch?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.92,0:23:11.06,Default,MASHA,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.06,0:23:14.60,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,Um, I can understand your confusion,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.60,0:23:17.37,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,but you should probably get dressed first.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.90,0:23:18.80,Default,MASHA,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.34,0:23:21.67,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Get dressed...?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.21,0:23:28.03,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,H-How did this happen?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.03,0:23:29.52,Default,MASHA,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.52,0:23:31.36,Default,CHISATO,0,0,0,,By the way, Kuze-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.36,0:23:32.44,Default,CHISATO,0,0,0,,You saw, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.22,0:23:37.22,Default,CHISATO,0,0,0,,Do you want a reset too?
